overview.en: SEC is the certificate of SkyEcoChain's entire ecosystem. It is currently a smart contract token under the erc20 standard. Its application scenario is to support the circulation in scenarios such as SEC wallet, Cloud City Tycoon, and SEC trading center.
overview.zh: SEC是 SkyEcoChain 整个大生态的通证证明，目前是在erc20的标准下的智能合约TOKEN，它的应用场景在于支持在SEC钱包、云城大亨、SEC交易中心等场景的流通。
